urls.notes: Bio: Austin Blanchfill is a worship leader, singer/songwriter, AI artist, and a creative entrepreneur whose mission is to point people to Jesus.

Video description: Some of my music is created using AI-assisted tools as part of the production process. This is one of those songs, and it is not my voice singing this song. I remain creatively and spiritually responsible for the message, lyrics, and direction of every song that I do, AI voice or my voice. AI is simply a tool that allows me to create and distribute music at scale, with excellence, and with the intention of pointing people to Jesus.
